<el-dropdown :show-timeout="100" trigger="click">
  <el-button plain>
    {{ !status?'启动':'停止' }}
    <i class="el-icon-caret-bottom el-icon--right" />
  </el-button>
  <el-dropdown-menu slot="dropdown" class="no-padding">
    <el-dropdown-item>
      <el-radio-group v-model="status" style="padding: 10px;">
        <el-radio :label="true">
          停止
        </el-radio>
        <el-radio :label="false">
         开启
        </el-radio>
      </el-radio-group>
    </el-dropdown-item>
  </el-dropdown-menu>
</el-dropdown>
